Paneer Taco 🌮🌯

Full recipe😍
Paneer - 100 gm 
Curd - 1/4 cup 
Salt 
Snapin Herbs 
Snapin Chilli flakes 
Snapin Kashmiri lal Mirch
Garam masala

Onions 
Capsicum 
Cabbage 
Salt 
Snapin herbs n chilli Flakes

For the Dip mix Green chutney n Hung Curd 

Firstly prepare a basic marination using curd along with the spices and coat the paneer well. Now let it sit for 15 mins, then cook it in a pan. Now prepare a basic sautee using veggies and @snapinindia Seasonings. After all the basic things are prepared take a half cooked roti and apply the green chutney hung curd sauce, veggies and paneer along with some cheese. 
Now apply some butter and cook on a tawa until crispy. 
Now your Taco is ready😍
